over 500
different languages?

36
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:06,436
However, uh,

37
00:03:06,471 --> 00:03:08,688
you ladies of the art
appreciation society

38
00:03:08,723 --> 00:03:12,442
will notice that their art
has a great unity.

39
00:03:12,477 --> 00:03:15,328
