for a specific purpose.

40
00:03:15,363 --> 00:03:18,448
Now, this one...
can you all see it?

41
00:03:18,483 --> 00:03:19,449
Now, this was made

42
00:03:19,484 --> 00:03:21,334
to frighten away
the evil spirits.

43
00:03:21,369 --> 00:03:23,203
And this one

44
00:03:23,238 --> 00:03:26,956
as a protection
against disease.

45
00:03:28,841 --> 00:03:31,094
Now, in my hand
here...

46
